    "description": "<u><strong>What is Raid Healing and what awaits you!</strong></u><br><br>Playtime: 10h+<br><br>Raid Healing is a healer game in which you take on the role of the main healer for your raid.<br><br>The game is based on classic MMO healer gameplay.<br>First you select a target to heal, this is done by clicking on a unit or using the mouse-over function. <br>By pressing a keybind or clicking on a button the desired heal is activated.<br><br>The goal of the game is to heal your raid against increasingly difficult enemy waves and to keep it alive until all enemies are defeated.<br><br><u><br><strong><br>How the game works</strong></u><br><br>Start a game and choose an area where you want to play.<br>Depending on the area the enemy waves will be composed of different unit classes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109650/extras/0b7367c0380c98629958fa8d0c3c1bb7.avif?t=1663948908\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Units</strong><br><br>Build your raid from 11 different classes and plan the lineup of your units for the battle.<br>If it is too hard take a priest to support you.<br>If you want to try something new you can add additional units of different classes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109650/extras/b50573e0c5275bb17e56c9a4de0310fa.avif?t=1663948908\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Abilities</strong><br><br>Select the abilities and heals you want to use in combat from the abilities list and <br>drag the abilities to your hot bars.<br>You can freely choose the keybindings for your hot bars.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109650/extras/422b98584fc3d47ce163429a2258f4e7.avif?t=1663948908\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><br><strong>User Interface</strong><br><br>Use the option to customize the user interface.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109650/extras/797bff172f6a14d82bad1e2c9f88e4c2.avif?t=1663948908\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><br><br><strong>Receive Equipment</strong><br><br>Receive equipment by defeating enemy units.<br>The equipment will be displayed to you in battle and automatically added to your inventory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109650/extras/0b842197d8da416c1a8e934db1f270a9.avif?t=1663948908\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Game Progress</strong><br><br>Gain experience for your units by defeating enemies and unlock higher area tiers.<br>If you choose the hardcore game mode all your units must survive to unlock the next tier.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109650/extras/d56f03749eba4bfe3a78f2101183b3b8.avif?t=1663948908\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Equip your Units</strong><br><br>After the battle equip your units with new or adjust the existing equipment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109650/extras/3e7bf3c1662573945116dd0d0984383c.avif?t=1663948908\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Equip the Player</strong><br><br>Change your equipment to unlock bonuses for your heals, change skill ranks or improve your stats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109650/extras/dd623668f1b4e291bbbaf66f7f37311b.avif?t=1663948908\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Modify Equipment</strong><br><br>Enchant, fuse or transfer set bonuses to customize all equipment according to your needs.<br><br><br><strong>If you like this then Raid Healing is a game for you!</strong>",
